title: Week 8 H.S. football picks
text:
Week 8 H.S. football picks Staff Report 8:12 p.m. EDT October 14, 2015 File photo CONNECT TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
We're getting close to the end of the regular season and it seems that some of our pickers have started their comeback. 
Ron Hartlaub went undefeated last week, giving him a chance to claw his way back into the top. Meanwhile, Eden Otero had some questionable picks that took her from being a contender, to tying her with last place. 
Joining the team this week, is another News Leader sports writer, Willa Grefe. She's a Robert E. Lee alum and the biggest soccer fan that anyone in Augusta County will ever encounter. 
So, without further ado, here are the weeks picks: 
Spotswood at Fort Defiance
